Assignment 1

Description:
This program logs messages from texts.txt, a pre-made text file containing lines of strings, into a log file (by default, messages.log).

Usage:
./driver [-h] [-t sec] [logfile]

Files:
driver.c, log.h, loglib.c, makefile, messages.log, README, texts.txt

References:
Program 2.7 in the textbook by Robbins & Robbins
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3053999/
https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/generating-random-number-range-c/
https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Example-of-Getopt.html

